1
00:00:00,900 --> 00:00:01,900
Hey, Michael.

2
00:00:02,102 --> 00:00:03,803
Yeah... they have my best wishes.

3
00:00:04,137 --> 00:00:05,338
He's got his own career now,

4
00:00:05,972 --> 00:00:07,572
and he's finally found where he belongs.

5
00:00:08,375 --> 00:00:10,553
I'd really appreciate it if you could
give them some positive coverage.

6
00:00:10,577 --> 00:00:11,945
Right... thanks a lot.

7
00:00:12,312 --> 00:00:13,312
Okay.

8
00:00:14,414 --> 00:00:15,414
Like the post first.

9
00:00:16,583 --> 00:00:18,417
It's the first time I've
seen one of our own artists

10
00:00:18,418 --> 00:00:19,719
post matching rings like this.

11
00:00:20,479 --> 00:00:22,280
They aren't worried
about losing fans at all.

12
00:00:23,957 --> 00:00:25,357
How should we respond to the press?

13
00:00:26,159 --> 00:00:27,259
Well, I'm just the "cousin" now.

14
00:00:27,260 --> 00:00:29,128
Hei Mingyan is his actual manager.

15
00:00:29,129 --> 00:00:30,963
Besides, I already told
the reporters to go to you.

16
00:00:30,964 --> 00:00:32,031
Me again?

17
00:00:32,032 --> 00:00:33,032
Xiaoan.

18
00:00:38,238 --> 00:00:39,238
What's this for?

19
00:00:39,639 --> 00:00:40,206
Are you giving this to me,

20
00:00:40,207 --> 00:00:41,417
or do you just want me to hold onto it?

21
00:00:41,441 --> 00:00:42,108
Hello?

22
00:00:42,409 --> 00:00:43,942
No, look, tell me...

23
00:00:43,943 --> 00:00:45,210
Yeah... I'd really
appreciate it if you could

24
00:00:45,211 --> 00:00:46,245
- keep the coverage positive.
- Just tell me...

25
00:00:46,246 --> 00:00:47,380
Thanks so much.

26
00:00:47,647 --> 00:00:48,314
Right...

27
00:00:48,315 --> 00:00:49,448
- I'd really appreciate some positive coverage.
- No, look, tell me...

28
00:00:49,449 --> 00:00:50,717
Okay, I owe you one.

29
00:01:01,594 --> 00:01:02,895
You still have to wear it, though.

30
00:01:02,896 --> 00:01:04,563
No, you put it on me.

31
00:01:04,564 --> 00:01:05,532
Put it on for me.

32
00:01:05,532 --> 00:01:06,532
Put it on.

33
00:01:06,933 --> 00:01:07,534
Help me put it on.

34
00:01:07,535 --> 00:01:08,567
You have to work, so wear it.

35
00:01:08,568 --> 00:01:09,335
Work, work, work.

36
00:01:09,336 --> 00:01:10,804
Put it on before you head out.

37
00:01:56,149 --> 00:01:57,149
Hei Yan.

38
00:01:57,750 --> 00:01:59,219
Wake up.

39
00:02:02,989 --> 00:02:04,524
It's going to be a circus today.

40
00:02:04,958 --> 00:02:06,798
The fans and the media
are losing their minds.

41
00:02:07,494 --> 00:02:09,662
You're my manager.

42
00:02:10,530 --> 00:02:11,810
Get up and handle the responses.

43
00:02:13,066 --> 00:02:14,133
I don't want to go.

44
00:02:14,134 --> 00:02:15,668
You go deal with them for me.
